Category:Imperial Navy pilots of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: "Duchess" was an Imperial TIE/sk x1 experimental air superiority fighter pilot during the Galactic Civil War. She had light skin and shoulder-length brown hair. Duchess had been stationed on Scarif, and during the resulting battle between Imperial and Rebel forces, she provided aerial support, flying over an All Terrain Armored Cargo Transport.
